//! Pub same-bare-name type fixture (wide layout). Exports a public `Gadget`
//! record whose sole field is an `i64`. Its sibling `hew::widgetpub8` exports a
//! public `Gadget` of the same bare name with an `i8` field — a divergent
//! layout. In the ambiguity oracle this module is plain-imported (exports
//! `Gadget` but does NOT publish it bare), so it must not poison a bare
//! `Gadget` reference that another module opted in.

/// Wide `Gadget`: a single `i64` field.
pub type Gadget {
    v: i64;
}
